<topic id="whr_accessible_tables_header_first_column">
  <title>Table with Header Cells in the First Column Only</title>
  <body>
    <p>For this type of table, you have to set the <codeph>@rowheader="firstcol"</codeph> attribute
      on the <xmlelement>table</xmlelement> element to identify the header column.</p>
    <table id="table_azh_wzm_sdb" rowheader="firstcol" colsep="1" rowsep="1" frame="all">
      <title> Example: Oxygen Events </title>
      <tgroup cols="4">
        <colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="1*"/>
        <colspec colname="COLSPEC1" colwidth="1.1*"/>
        <colspec colname="newCol3" colwidth="1*"/>
        <colspec colname="newCol4" colwidth="1*"/>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>Event</entry>
            <entry>Evolution of TC 2018</entry>
            <entry>Markup UK</entry>
            <entry>Balisage 2018 - The Markup Conference</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Date</entry>
            <entry>May 31 - June 1, 2018</entry>
            <entry>June 9 - 10, 2018</entry>
            <entry>July 31 - August 3, 2018</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Location</entry>
            <entry>Sofia, Bulgaria</entry>
            <entry>London, United Kingdom</entry>
            <entry>Rockville, Maryland, USA</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
    <p>
      <codeblock outputclass="language-xml">&lt;table rowheader="firstcol" colsep="1" rowsep="1" frame="all">
  &lt;title>
    &lt;b>Oxygen Events&lt;/b>
  &lt;/title>
  &lt;tgroup cols="4">
    &lt;colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="1*"/>
    &lt;colspec colname="COLSPEC1" colwidth="1.1*"/>
    &lt;colspec colname="newCol3" colwidth="1*"/>
    &lt;colspec colname="newCol4" colwidth="1*"/>
    &lt;tbody>
      &lt;row>
        &lt;entry>Event&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>Evolution of TC 2018&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>Markup UK&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>Balisage 2018 - The Markup Conference&lt;/entry>
      &lt;/row>
      &lt;row>
        &lt;entry>Date&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>May 31 - June 1, 2018&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>June 9 - 10, 2018&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>July 31 - August 3, 2018&lt;/entry>
      &lt;/row>
      &lt;row>
        &lt;entry>Location&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>Sofia, Bulgaria&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>London, United Kingdom&lt;/entry>
        &lt;entry>Rockville, Maryland, USA&lt;/entry>
      &lt;/row>
    &lt;/tbody>
  &lt;/tgroup>
&lt;/table></codeblock>
    </p>
  </body>
